   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="edition" ana="#b1" xml:lang="grc" subtype="transcription" xml:id="zoor0357.transcription" corresp="#zoor0357.translation">
            <p><expan><abbr>Κ</abbr><ex>ύρι</ex><abbr>ε</abbr></expan>, <choice><corr>τῷ</corr><sic>ὁ</sic></choice> <choice><corr>γράψαντι</corr><sic>γράψας</sic></choice>
               <lb/><space quantity="1" unit="character"/> δὸς <space extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
               <lb/>χάρησμα <expan><abbr>β</abbr><ex>όλια</ex></expan>
               <num value="2" xml:lang="lat">I<unclear>I</unclear></num></p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="zoor0357.translation" corresp="#zoor0357.transcription">
            <p>Lord, grant the person<lb/>who wrote (this)<lb/>two throws of the dice.</p>
         </div>
      <div type="edition" subtype="transcription_segmented"><p><w xml:id="zoor0392-1" xml:lang="grc"><expan><abbr>Κ</abbr><ex>ύρι</ex><abbr>ε</abbr></expan>,</w> <w xml:id="zoor0392-2" xml:lang="grc"><choice><corr>τῷ</corr><sic>ὁ</sic></choice></w> <w xml:id="zoor0392-3" xml:lang="grc"><choice><corr>γράψαντι</corr><sic>γράψας</sic></choice></w> <w xml:id="zoor0392-4" xml:lang="grc">δὸς</w> <w xml:id="zoor0392-5" xml:lang="grc">χάρησμα</w> <w xml:id="zoor0392-6" xml:lang="grc"><expan><abbr>β</abbr><ex>όλια</ex></expan></w> <num xml:id="zoor0392-7" value="2" xml:lang="lat">I<unclear>I</unclear></num></p>
</div>
</body>
      <back>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Two vertical lines at end of line three may stand for the Latin number II. The entire
               slab may have served as a race game, with players aiming at a finish line according
               to the outcome of the dice.</p>
         </div>
